snippet.title: Knight Terrors Switch Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Knight Terrors is an all-new horror-themed arcade-style side-scroller, just in time for tricks or treats!

Developed by FreakZone Games and Nicalis Inc., and published by Nicalis, Knight Terrors will launch on Nintendo Switch October 24th digitally via the Nintendo eShop.
